  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetic Study of AEB071 in Patients Following Liver Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Two-period, Multi-center, Single Dose Study to Assess the Pharmacokinetics of AEB071 in de Novo Liver Transplant Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
